title: #92Noon! Lavelle in for PA!
description: Lavelle is heavy on Twins and baseball today. Twins AAA Rochester vox Josh Wetzel joins, Michael Russo in studio for a couple segments, Gophers baseball coach John Anderson on the hotline, and Twins P Jake Odorizzi closes the show!
